Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:50.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my friend, aren't you? You're "her."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I... loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:58.14,Main,,0,0,0,,We took a photo of us together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,We drank Mom's honey ginger\Nmilk and sang the love song.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:11.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so warm. You must still have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Only the bear who killed\NMom could have that pendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:37.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikumaaaaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:45.52,Main,,0,0,0,,"BRIDE-IN-THE-BOX"\N{\i1}Viens avec moi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:48.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Church chimes echo in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:51.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offer up a prayer and betray today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wander in a dark forest, then become{\i0}\N{\i1}the morning moon at the Wall of Severance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't join the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:03.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I've made you stickier{\i0}\N{\i1}with sweet, thin honey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:07.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, approve me, I'll be a good girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture-book pages dancing on{\i0}\N{\i1}the breeze shake up shadowy memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting you-know-where,{\i0}\N{\i1}in an empty world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everything falls apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to gracefully writhe,{\i0}\N{\i1}even if you have to bend space-time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:40.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flower petals will slowly{\i0}\N{\i1}enfold us on a starry night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}J'ai besoin de toi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:13.07,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Approximately 20 Years Ago・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I was once an unwanted bear,\Nabandoned in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That was when I met Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:36.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll shelter you.\NThis school is my "box."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:42.76,Main,,0,0,0,,He liked boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:49.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuriika, this world sullies anything pure, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,If I do this, the flower\Ncan stay unsullied for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:04:00.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You see, in this world,\Nonly the unsullied has value.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Purrowr! Purrowr!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:11.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so beautiful, Yuriika. You're special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,My most especially precious treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I went in his box.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:28.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Inside his box, I was an especially\Nprecious, unsullied creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:31.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I was an unwanted bear no longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I've found my next\Nwonderfully unsullied creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.37,Main,,0,0,0,,So I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,My precious one, don't abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:52.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Purrowr!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I understood, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:03.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to box up your precious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:07.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Or else they'll walk right out of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll be sullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:14.52,Main,,0,0,0,,From now on, this is my box.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you cutting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,If I don't cut them before they're\Nsullied, I can't put them in a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Why box them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:36.09,Main,,0,0,0,,To protect my pure,\Nprecious things from the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:42.72,Main,,0,0,0,,My box lets me be special.\NIf you're un-special...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're unwanted, no one will find--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You... found me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:56.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. So unbox yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:06:00.49,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't open the box, look\Nat your precious things, and touch them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:03.82,Main,,0,0,0,,it's the same as not having them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.03,Main,,0,0,0,,The same as not having...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:10.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm empty. The world is invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Open up your boxes and\Nshow me your precious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:34.48,Main,,0,0,0,,And so Reia and I became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:39.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia gave color to my blank, invisible world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:49.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I found all sorts of precious things with Reia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:56.37,Main,,0,0,0,,And she let herself be sullied with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia, do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I love you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be friends forever, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Friends forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:32.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuriika!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:37.92,Main,,0,0,0,,This is proof of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,A pledge to never forget love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't forget love,\Nyou'll never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.84,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't give up on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:49.01,Main,,0,0,0,,even if you lose something,\Nyou'll never be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia, I love you. I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:08:02.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew all along that Reia's\Nlove was different from mine. I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:08.03,Main,,0,0,0,,But even still, I wallowed\Nin that sweet, fleeting dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:11.53,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"17 Years Ago・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:19.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Her name is "Kureha"! It means "red wing."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:21.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop that, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,She really loves this pendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:30.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, Kureha, say hi to Mama's dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:40.64,Main,,0,0,0,,See, didn't I tell you? You have\Nto box up all your precious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:44.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Otherwise they'll be sullied. You'll lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:48.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Now Reia's love has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:54.70,Main,,0,0,0,,That baby took it from you because\N{\i1}you {\i0}foolishly left your box and got sullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Babies are the purest\Nthings in this world, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.14,Main,,0,0,0,,...give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sullied, so I'm empty. I'm invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not precious enough to box up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:40.41,Main,,0,0,0,,So now I am a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:46.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I've become an empty box,\Njust wishing for something to fill my void.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The stars rained down\Non the still-invisible world
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:55.43,Main,,0,0,0,,and the Wall of Severance was formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,We can never go back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:16.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia... Reia... Reia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Fulfill me! Fill in my gaps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:24.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so lonely! Please, Reia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:32.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Take this pendant with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:36.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a love charm. I know it will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Purrowr...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you give that pendant away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:48.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you love that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,No! She's Kureha's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:56.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. You threw the\Nproof of our friendship, purrowr...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:11:00.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You threw my love away! Purroooowrrrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:06.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Chomp, chomp, purrowr.\NChomp, chomp, purrowr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Chomp, chomp, purrowr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Chomp, chomp, purrowr.\NChomp, chomp, purrowr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:13.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I ate Reia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:18.55,Main,,0,0,0,,To put her in the box of myself.\NThat would fulfill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:21.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Or so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:34.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Even after eating Reia, I was still starved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,The emptiness in me wasn't filled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I was interrogating her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,And how did she answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:47.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:55.67,Main,,0,0,0,,That pendant disappeared\Nthe night Mom was killed by a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:59.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you have it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:01.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:05.64,Main,,0,0,0,,She just said, "I can't tell you right now,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:09.94,Main,,0,0,0,,and then this morning,\Nthey were both gone without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Undeniable proof those two\Nare bears disguised as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:24.99,Main,,0,0,0,,And Ginko Yurishiro,\Nthe one with Reia's pendant, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,The bear that killed Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:29.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You were young, and she got close\Nto you by saying she was your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:39.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Then she killed the one\Nmost precious to you: Reia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't expect love or friendship\Nfrom them. You have to exclude them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Exclude them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:51.15,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:58.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You stole Reia's love from me,\Nand now you'll pay for that with your flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:05.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't escape now. Kureha Tsubaki,\Nyou're going to be my boxed bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.13,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.09,Main,,0,0,0,,"To the Criminal-Bear"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:30.48,Main,,0,0,0,,"Ginko Yurishiro, I know the\Ngrave crime you committed. You are"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:39.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko, how about we go back\Nto the other side of the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter how true your love is,\Nwhen she knows you're a bear,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin {\i0}won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Promise Kisses only exist in picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumaria is the goddess of the wall!\NHer job is to separate bears and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:01.84,Main,,0,0,0,,She'd never make us friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I made you give up kisses, Lulu.\NI won't go back now, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:11.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if it means a grave sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:16.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. I know what you did, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:21.40,Main,,0,0,0,,So let's go home! If Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}\Nfinds out, you can't get love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,But you can't do a Promise Kiss\Nwithout telling her the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:30.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go home! Ginko, even if\Nyou give up on love, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I can't ever kiss.\NAs long as you're with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.13,Main,,0,0,0,,"Incoming Call: Blocked Number"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:55.44,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a challenge from the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:15:01.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki,\Nif your love is true, go to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:04.49,Main,,0,0,0,,The bears are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:05.86,Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:15.79,Main,,0,0,0,,We were friends... I loved her, but she...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:19.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:25.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait, Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:31.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you still love Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}!\NGrowl! Just don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:35.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko! Ginko! Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:40.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Give yourself over to the humans,\Nand your love will be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:43.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:45.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:47.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,She's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:59.08,Main,,0,0,0,,But was this really right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:03.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh, why not? At least\Nwe'll find out whose love is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.22,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's horribly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:10.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Order, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,We dwell in the space\Nbetween human and bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,All must be as Kumaria wills it.\NThat is the sexy way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it will rain. Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.57,Main,,0,0,0,,The time has come at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Now come here, Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I cast aside beardom\Nand became human for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.09,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:47.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant-bear Yuriika Hakonaka, I ask you:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:53.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you give up on boxes?\NOr will you give up on love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:56.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't give up on boxes. I'll give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Please make me a human!\NI want to watch Kureha Tsubaki grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:07.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia's love is inside that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:11.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to fill the box of myself with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You won't regret it? If you do that,\Nyou're doomed to be a box for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:23.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia gave my love to some\Nother cub like it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:25.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:29.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. I shall now declare the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:32.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:38.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.23,Main,,0,0,0,,The bear opens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:50.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss... Yuriika...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,She's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,She is the bear who killed Reia.\NShe's our mortal enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.55,Main,,0,0,0,,My mother's killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:17.47,Main,,0,0,0,,She claimed to be your friend,\Nand she {\i1}tricked {\i0}you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:21.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That's how she stole\Nthe one most precious to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:28.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You ate my...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:32.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't eat her, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why do you have that pendant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother gave it to me.\NShe said it was a love charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Love charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:49.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a bear. But we were friends anyway, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:54.55,Main,,0,0,0,,But then one day,\Nwe couldn't be together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:19:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You started to think of bears\Nas humans' enemies, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Obviously. Bears kill people--killed\Nmy mother! They're all enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:12.11,Main,,0,0,0,,No! I was an unwanted bear, but you found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:16.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You approved me and gave me love, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:19.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the love I got that day.\NI won't give up on the love I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I crossed the wall.\NFor you, Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:34.59,Main,,0,0,0,,To become true friends with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,True... friends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't listen, Kureha!\NShe's a liar, a murderer-bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She {\i0}killed the girls in our class!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,To protect Kureha from the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:51.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive those who exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a bear. That's all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.28,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:20:00.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you? Bears feel no love or friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,They're sullied beasts! That's their true nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:06.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on, shoot her to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:16.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I finally get it. When Kumaria\Ntold me about the "Promise Kiss,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:20.43,Main,,0,0,0,,she meant your bullet, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:27.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll accept it as a criminal-bear.\NThat'll prove my love's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:32.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the only way to\Nbecome true friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:36.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you hesitating for?!\NPunish the criminal-bear, {\i1}now{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:43.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me the Promise Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:21:02.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Promise... Kiss? From me to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,And me to you. Then everything\Nwill awaken, and everything will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:27.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't shoot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:32.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Killing her won't bring Mom back.\NIt won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:43.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You mustn't forgive her! Give this\Nwoman-eating bear the bullet of judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,But she... But {\i1}Ginko {\i0}saved me\Nfrom the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:54.44,Main,,0,0,0,,She jumped into the fire and risked\Nher life to protect Sumika's letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:58.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You little fool. She's just a\Ncriminal-bear pretending to be pure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:21:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Still!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:02.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:07.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}, I know what Ginko did to Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:19.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. Ginko committed a grave crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:22.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko was Sumika's--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:49.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.95,0:22:51.95,Main,,0,0,0,,...never forgive bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:04.22,Main,,0,0,0,,"Is your love the real thing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the boundary that severed{\i0}\N{\i1}ripe moon from sleeping forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:38.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the law God shackles us with and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:45.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned away from the bleating flock{\i0}\N{\i1}of shadows and howled my bloodthirsty ego{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here amidst the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Overflowing honey and soul{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.48,0:23:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to rend silk with my fangs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:05.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid you'll vanish{\i0}\N{\i1}like the world's last ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:12.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The savage beast inside me{\i0}\N{\i1}tore out the throat of innocence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:22.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, shoot me through the heart{\i0}\N{\i1}with your sweet-scented Barrett of love{\i0}
